latestIgtvVideos.title: We are the world❤ | Michael Jackson 🙏🙌 | Just an attempt
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Wanted to attempt a song for World Music Day which depicts love, peace and happiness as music is the only way to express what we actually feel deep inside. Suddenly this song hit my mind and I remember this song being taught by our music teacher back when I was in school. The words are so beautifully crafted, yet so simple to express and understand.This song in particular has always touched my heart and I genuinely feel "We all are part of God's great big family....and the only truth is love which we all need.."
Be positive stay positive and spread positivity around ❣🥰
#muchlove
#latepost
#worldmusicdayspecial 
#happyvibes

Had the incredible honor of performing with @thelive100experience in Surat for none other than India’s biggest business tycoon and the king of the diamond industry, Shri Savji Dholakia! A truly grand celebration for his son’s post-wedding event—an unforgettable night of music, energy, and pure magic!

This show was truly special as I reunited with @thelive100experience once again! Coming off the high of our outstanding Guinness World Record achievement, this performance was nothing short of extraordinary! Endless memories and friendship that I carried forward with me and also learnt a lot about music and art. 

Thank you @chaitanyashinde97 @shivikarajesh for having me on board! ❤🤗 Excited for many more incredible moments ahead!
